<prompt>

## Context

A large B2B SaaS company in Russia is looking for ideas how to attract entrepreneurs who have not registered a legal entity yet, but plan to do so soon.


## Research Goal

Опиши способы привлечения пользователей, которые используют продукты из списка из файлов longlist1-4.md


## Research Requirements
- Company facts must rely on trustworthy sources: official press releases, company websites, reputable news coverage, investor materials, or regulatory filings.
- The research must be maximally evidence-based.
- All conclusions must be derived strictly from data.
- If open data is not found, ничего не придумывай, просто не пиши про это
- Every conclusion must include links to its data sources.
- The research and the final report must be written entirely in the Russian language.
- Based on discovery method, JTBD, and effectiveness, explain which attraction type best fits and why.

## как исследовать

For each product from list:

<опиши продукт из списка>
  <product_name></product_name>
  <product_url></product_url>
  <описание из источников longlist1-4.md>
  <product_attraction_analysis>
</опиши продукт из списка>
<способы привлечения>
Analyze all non-direct ways the product attracts and acquires users:
    Paid Tripwire,
    Free Tripwire,
    Community / Membership,
    First-customer acquisition,
    Ecosystem lock-in,
    Data dependency,
    Sandbox / demo environments,
    Pay-after-result,
    Celebrity or expert involvement,
    Closed access,
    Event marketing,
    Data-as-an-entry,
    User certification,
    Embedded acquisition,
    Educational platforms
    Content marketing
</способы привлечения>
<описание способов привлечения>
опиши способы привлечения пользователей в этот продукт
  <attraction_mechanisms>
  <jtbd>
  <capacity_analysis>
</описание способов привлечения>

## ✅ Condition
<condition>
Return the result in .doc and .pdf.
Provide answers for the user in Russian.
</condition>

</prompt>


